{
  "stem": "1721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 418.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I mean, we were called dirty kikes, even though we were living in the Lower East Side of New York.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't care where it went, it happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But, it wasn't as traumatic, because we had a safe haven to go back, and we had friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We knew that-- we knew there was just-- you know, we knew that it wasn't sanctioned by the authorities like it was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism wasn't?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, 0 wasn't very large then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was tall, but I was skinny.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't overpowering.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was just tall and gangly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I came to-- when I was-- I think when I was 15 or 16 years old, I may have been six foot tall, but I must have weighed 130 pounds.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I was just a bag of beans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My nutrition just never-- it just never caught up with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so, I never had any not very much flesh, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, but I learned to fight in the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, I learned to take care of myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Growing up in New York, you had to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You had the opportunity to do it, and I think I had a little training in Germany, but you really can't defend yourself against five or 10 kids who really had in their mind to-- but once I came to New York, it was a little different.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I got a little more confidence in myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So, that was basically my Jewish background, I mean, right after the war, right after the camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, life was pretty bad for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Life was pretty bad for me, and my mother just really-- just didn't like me very much.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
